# Kaaval Kani - Crime Analysis & Prediction System ( Tuticorin )

## Overview
Kaaval Kani is an intelligent crime analysis and prediction system designed specifically for Tuticorin, Tamil Nadu. The system processes Tamil-language crime reports and distress calls to provide real-time insights and predictive analytics for law enforcement.

## Features
- Tamil PDF processing with OCR capabilities
- Tamil Natural Language Processing for data extraction
- Real-time crime hotspot visualization
- Predictive analytics using LSTM and XGBoost
- Interactive crime heatmaps
- Live alert system
- Historical trend analysis

## Technology Stack
- **Backend:** Python (FastAPI)
- **Frontend:** React.js
- **Database:** PostgreSQL
- **Maps:** Leaflet.js/Google Maps API
- **ML Models:** LSTM, XGBoost
- **OCR & NLP:** Custom Tamil language processing
